1
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:30,960
Shen Jingyao.

2
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:35,840
I hope the knife you handed me is sharp enough.

3
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,880
Back then,

4
00:01:47,479 --> 00:01:49,680
I held you when you were just a month old,

5
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:54,160
and knelt in the Lu family's backyard until my knees bled

6
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:57,080
before they let us in.

7
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,920
I have endured everything until today,

8
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,200
just to

9
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:04,640
put you in the position of heir.

10
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:09,280
Now even God is helping me.

11
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:13,260
Not only will I kick Shen Zhixia out of the house,

12
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,640
but I will also make your good father

13
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,520
turn against your good brother.

14
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:24,880
You are the only one who can be the heir of the Lu family.

15
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,920
I was wondering why Shen Zhixia

16
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:29,720
has been acting like a different person recently.

17
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,940
Once I take over the Lu family,

18
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:37,120
I will set fire to that backyard.

19
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,780
You will praise me, right?

20
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,640
Burn it if you want to.

21
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,850
The whole Lu family belongs to you anyway.

22
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,680
You must remember,

23
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:52,960
everything I do is for you.

24
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,120
Jingxi.

25
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:13,680
Zhenye.

26
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:17,340
With so many things happening at home recently,

27
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,480
I feel so exhausted.

28
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,520
Only when I'm with you

29
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:25,120
can I feel a bit more relaxed.

30
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:31,320
It's been hard on you lately.

31
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,880
I prepared some wine for you.

32
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,960
It's your favorite.

33
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,400
To help you sleep.

34
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:40,250
You're always the most considerate to me.

35
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,500
I'll go back to the room first.

36
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,880
Take your time drinking. No rush.

37
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,240
Manyun.

38
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,960
You look so beautiful today.

39
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,440
Dad.

40
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:17,519
Dad.

41
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:19,360
Why are you hiding?

42
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,320
Dad, you're drunk.

43
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,779
You have the wrong person.

44
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,720
Zhenye, hurry.

45
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,260
What's wrong with you?

46
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,600
Get up.

47
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,280
It's okay.

48
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,120
Shen Zhixia.

49
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,880
What are you doing?

50
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,880
You're wearing my clothes

51
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,610
to seduce your father-in-law?

52
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,840
Crazy, crazy.

53
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,080
I think you're really crazy.

54
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,600
You told me there was a banquet to attend

55
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,330
and asked me to try on the dress.

56
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,360
I was wondering

57
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:49,159
what you had up your sleeve.

58
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,680
Turns out it was such a dirty scheme.

59
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:54,080
What nonsense are you talking about?

60
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,120
Dare you deny it?

61
00:04:58,640 --> 00:04:59,440
Zhixia.

62
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,880
We are hosting a family banquet tomorrow night.

63
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,840
I think this dress is quite nice.

64
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:04,840
Try it on.

65
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,920
Judging by the size,

66
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,520
it must be your dress.

67
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:25,960
It was my favorite dress when I was young.

68
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,530
It doesn't fit anymore.

69
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,000
I think this dress

70
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,320
suits you quite well.

71
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,680
Why don't you try it on?

72
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,340
We still have time to alter it.

73
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:39,720
You personally handed me the dress,

74
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,720
deliberately making Dad mistake me for someone else.

75
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,840
I only fought back in self-defense.

76
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:46,360
Shen Zhixia, stop acting.

77
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,480
I kept quiet

78
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,280
to save you some dignity.

79
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,520
And yet

80
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,370
you put the blame on me, huh?

81
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,720
Zhenye, take a good look.

82
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:02,240
I think it's time to treat

83
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,280
your paranoia.

84
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:06,680
How did she get these medical records?

85
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,120
You are a lunatic.

86
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:16,010
I can't believe you kept it from the Lu family for so long.

87
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,120
Hurry,

88
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,960
lock her up

89
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:22,040
and send her to the psychiatric hospital tomorrow morning.

90
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,680
Yes.

91
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,480
Let's see who dares to touch her.

92
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,440
Jingheng.

93
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,400
Go.

94
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:56,640
Go after them.

95
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,520
Get in the car.

96
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:21,680
Hurry up.

97
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:23,920
Don't move.

98
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,280
Lu Jingheng,

99
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:32,040
are you really going to go crazy

100
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,440
with that woman?

101
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,040
You're going to anger me to death.

102
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,840
Zhenye, don't be angry.

103
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,560
Jingheng

104
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:42,760
is blinded by Zhixia.

105
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,360
For an outsider,

106
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:47,250
he doesn't even care about the Lu family's rules.

107
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,840
Brother.

108
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,380
Your approach is indeed inappropriate.

109
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,520
It's one thing for Shen Zhixia to be crazy normally,

110
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,520
but this time she framed our dad.

111
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,720
You still defend her so much.

112
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,680
Do you want Dad to take the blame?

113
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:14,240
I'll give you one more chance.

114
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,040
Tomorrow,

115
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:19,410
you will personally send this crazy woman

116
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:21,160
to the mental hospital.

117
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,520
If you are unwilling,

118
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,720
the Lu family's business

119
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:28,400
will have absolutely nothing to do with you.

120
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:30,560
Dad, I can't possibly

121
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,159
send her to a place like that.

122
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:32,840
You!

123
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:39,720
Fine.

124
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,240
I will make you remember clearly

125
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,400
that in the Lu family,

126
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,160
you don't call the shots.

127
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,260
Enforce the family rules!

128
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:24,160
This time, Su Manyun

129
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:27,040
is deliberately trying to drag Lu Zhenye down.

130
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,120
In the Lu family,

131
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:30,080
touching Lu Zhenye's interests

132
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:32,480
is crossing an absolute red line.

133
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:35,880
Lu Jingheng won't be able to protect me even if he wants to.

134
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:38,880
But how did my medical records

135
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:40,480
end up with Su Manyun?

136
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,120
Could it be Shen Jingyao?

137
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,840
Miss Wen.

138
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,280
Why are you here?

139
00:09:58,680 --> 00:09:59,720
Are you alright?

140
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,200
Jingheng said something happened to you.

141
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,680
He asked me to find you first,

142
00:10:02,680 --> 00:10:04,810
and arrange for you to hide at my place.

143
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,880
What exactly happened?

144
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:11,840
Come home with me first.

145
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,370
We can talk about it at home.

146
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,520
Freshly made rose pastry.

147
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,080
Have a taste

148
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,010
to tide you over.

149
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:44,520
I thought you didn't like rose pastries.

150
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,850
Changed your taste?

151
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,280
Shen Zhixia.

152
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:02,520
You don't think the score between us

153
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:04,240
is settled, do you?

154
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,880
You colluded with Su Manyun.

155
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:15,770
You didn't think I was serious about you, did you?

156
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:19,330
It's time to go back to the Lu family for your punishment.

157
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,240
Catch them.

158
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,520
Stop!

159
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,080
Hurry!

160
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,080
Shen Zhixia.

161
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:38,520
The things you pretend to forget,

162
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,850
I will definitely help you remember them.

163
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,640
Don't worry, Zhenye.

164
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:48,160
I've been at the hospital.

165
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,320
She hasn't woken up yet.

166
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,320
You're right.

167
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,280
If she wakes up

168
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,680
and remembers what happened that night,

169
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:59,320
she might go around telling everyone.

170
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,440
Then our whole Lu family

171
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:03,120
will lose face in our circle.

172
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,320
When she wakes up,

173
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,440
I will call the psychiatric hospital directly

174
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,970
and have them take her away.

175
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:11,200
She won't have a chance to talk nonsense out there.

176
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:13,080
I'll keep a close eye on her.

177
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,840
What Lu Zhenye cares about most

178
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,440
is indeed his scandal.

179
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:20,520
In that case...

180
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,720
Mrs. Lu.

181
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,040
Currently, the patient's

182
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:27,720
vital signs are all stable.

183
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:30,080
Fortunately, there is no serious problem.

184
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,200
After the patient wakes up,

185
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,920
we will do a comprehensive examination.

186
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:33,560
Okay.

187
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,840
Where am I?

188
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:38,920
Miss Shen,

189
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:39,760
this is the hospital.

190
00:12:39,760 --> 00:12:40,800
What's wrong with you?

191
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:41,720
Who are you?

192
00:12:42,040 --> 00:12:43,880
I want my family.

193
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,280
Miss Shen,

194
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,680
this is your family member.

195
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:47,000
Zhixia.

196
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,360
I don't know you.

197
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,040
I want to go home.

198
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:49,440
Shen Zhixia!

199
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,800
I want to go home.

200
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:51,400
Shen Zhixia.

201
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:52,360
I want to go home.

202
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:54,960
I want to go home. I want to go home.

203
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,960
Who are you?

204
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,880
Shen Zhixia,

205
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,760
do you know me or not?

206
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,280
Let me go.

207
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,520
Stop playing the fool.

208
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:06,920
Tell me.

209
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:08,320
Do you know me?

210
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,120
Who exactly am I?

211
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,880
Let go.

212
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:11,520
Jingheng.

213
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,280
Because of her,

214
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,800
you've opposed the family again and again.

215
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:16,060
Take a good look at her.

216
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,360
She's already crazy.

217
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:19,540
She doesn't even know who you are.

218
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:20,440
Are you still going to go against your father

219
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,720
because of her?

220
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:24,320
I don't care if she knows anyone.

221
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:25,280
She is my wife.

222
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,000
I'll take care of her for the rest of her life.

223
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,860
None of you can lay a finger on her.

224
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,000
Who are you?

225
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,080
Put me down.

226
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:33,080
Who are you?

227
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:39,320
What's your name?

228
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:44,480
What is this?

229
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:46,920
This is red ink.

230
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,320
